snippet.title: Apple IIGS Longplay - Arkanoid
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the game Arkanoid for Apple IIGS computers, developed by Taito in 1988. The game is very good arcade port of the breakout clone. Enjoy it in Full HD60p.
